Either \f(CW\*(C`fake\*(C'\fR or \f(CW\*(C`uring\*(C'\fR. Defaults to \f(CW\*(C`fake\*(C'\fR.
.IP \(bu 4
\&\f(CW\*(C`clock\*(C'\fR
.Sp
Clock object used for timeout calculations. It must provide \f(CWtick()\fR and
\&\f(CWnow_ns()\fR.
.IP \(bu 4
\&\f(CW\*(C`queue_size\*(C'\fR
.Sp
Queue depth hint used by the backend.
